      "QuestionTypeId": 0,
      "QuestionId": 86854,
      "Explanation": "Mean = (12 + 15 + 18 + 22 + 25 + 28 + 30) / 7 \u2248 21.43<br><br>Squared differences from the mean:<br>(12 - 21.43)^2 \u2248 89.19<br>(15 - 21.43)^2 \u2248 41.03<br>(18 - 21.43)^2 \u2248 11.69<br>(22 - 21.43)^2 \u2248 0.33<br>(25 - 21.43)^2 \u2248 12.89<br>(28 - 21.43)^2 \u2248 42.77<br>(30 - 21.43)^2 \u2248 73.24<br><br>Variance = (89.19 + 41.03 + 11.69 + 0.33 + 12.89 + 42.77 + 73.24) / 7 \u2248 35.04<br>Standard Deviation = \u221aVariance \u2248 \u221a35.04 \u2248 5.93",
      "Answer": "A",
      "Marks": 0
    },
